    "发布到 VD社区，表示你同意以下社区公约：\n\n• 你对自己发布的内容负责，并拥有发布它的权利。\n• 严禁发布令人反感的内容——包括色情或露骨性内容、暴力血腥、仇恨或歧视、骚扰或欺凌、违法内容、自残等。VoiceDrop 对令人反感的内容和滥用行为零容忍。\n• 违规内容一经举报将被立即下架，并在 24 小时内处理；屡次或严重违规的账号将被移除。\n• 你可以随时举报不当内容、屏蔽不想看到的用户。\n\n继续即表示你已阅读并同意本社区公约与最终用户许可协议（EULA）。如需联系或投诉内容，请发邮件至 %@。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Posting to the VD Community means you agree to the community guidelines:\n\n• You are responsible for what you post and must have the right to post it.\n• Objectionable content is strictly prohibited — including pornographic or sexually explicit material, graphic violence, hate or discrimination, harassment or bullying, illegal content, self-harm, and the like. VoiceDrop has zero tolerance for objectionable content and abusive behavior.\n• Reported content is taken down immediately and handled within 24 hours; accounts with repeated or serious violations will be removed.\n• You can report inappropriate content or block users you don't want to see at any time.\n\nBy continuing, you confirm you have read and agree to these community guidelines and the End User License Agreement (EULA). To contact us or complain about content, email %@."
          }
        }
      }
    },
