    "还没成文": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No article yet"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "还没有写作风格。\n\n把蒸馏好的文风贴进来，挖文章时会带上它、让文章更像你；或者让 Claude 用「蒸馏文风」从你已发的文章里提炼一份。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No writing style yet.\n\nPaste in a distilled writing style — mining will use it so articles sound more like you. Or have Claude distill one from articles you've already published."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "还没有写作风格版本。\n先去设置 → 写作风格里保存一份。": {
      "localizations": {
