            "value": "No articles yet"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "这个名字会出现在文章署名，以及挖文章时对你的称呼。随时可改。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This name appears in your article byline, and it's what we call you when mining articles. Change it anytime."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "这条录音的文件损坏了，没法转写。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This recording's file is corrupted and can't be transcribed."
