    },
    "这条录音里没有识别到说话声。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No speech was detected in this recording."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "这段录音听到了，只是没找到能单独成篇的内容——可能太零碎，或者还没说成一件事。把想法讲完整一点、重录一段试试。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We heard this recording, but couldn't find anything that stands on its own as an article — it may be too fragmented, or not yet shaped into one idea. Try recording again with a more complete thought."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "这段录音太短，没攒够能成文的内容。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This recording is too short — not enough content to write up."
